Anorther problem could be …

If ya rebooted your server sometimes
your Gatway ir IPv4 has changed i’m thaking about the

192.168.1.**

If that number changed …
check at CMD - /ipconfig
If it is!

Than go back to your router page – 192.168.1.1 And go to yout Setup of your server (i dont know what router you got)
Than change it to 192.168.1.** - ** = New number after your IPv4

Also Vista users can go to Network right klik on their router
than the have to choise settings… When u clicked that go to settings … and than change your
server info to the Right Ipv4 …

Grtzz Wattzz.
